  ('locality-1fb53453-moex-00274', 'locality-1fb53453', 'locality-1fb53453-moex-110-51f0585d', 'sub-locality-1fb53453-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列關於通貨膨脹之敘述何者正確？', '["嚴重通貨膨脹可能緣起於戰爭或其他造成政府長時間入不敷出的預算赤字", "失業率和通貨膨脹率有抵換的關係存在，時間越久越明顯", "體系發生未預期到之通貨膨脹會對債權人有利而對債務人不利", "如果A國的通貨膨脹率長期高於B國通貨膨脹率，則A國貨幣會相對於B國升值"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:34:35+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "9a3f62f137b0", "answer_pdf_sha1": "d6448fd149c5", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110190", "c": "317", "s": "1301", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "經濟學概論與財政學概論", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年特種考試地方政府公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 10, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "locality", "civil_category": "財經廉政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('locality-1fb53453-moex-00275', 'locality-1fb53453', 'locality-1fb53453-moex-110-51f0585d', 'sub-locality-1fb53453-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '完全競爭市場下，X財貨的供給具完全彈性，假設對X財貨的買方課稅，每單位X課徵$T，下 列敘述何者正確？', '["X財貨的銷售量不變", "租稅的超額負擔為零", "相較於稅前，賣方收到的價格減少$T", "相較於稅前，買方支付的價格（包含稅）增加$T"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:34:35+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "9a3f62f137b0", "answer_pdf_sha1": "d6448fd149c5", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110190", "c": "317", "s": "1301", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "經濟學概論與財政學概論", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年特種考試地方政府公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 11, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "locality", "civil_category": "財經廉政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('locality-1fb53453-moex-00276', 'locality-1fb53453', 'locality-1fb53453-moex-110-51f0585d', 'sub-locality-1fb53453-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '已知某福利金領取者，不工作時每月可以獲得$10,000福利金；若工作所得超過$5,000，每增加$1 的收入，福利金將減少$0.5。試問工作所得超過多少，即不再享有補助利益？', '["$10,000", "$15,000", "$20,000", "$25,000"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:34:35+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "9a3f62f137b0", "answer_pdf_sha1": "d6448fd149c5", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110190", "c": "317", "s": "1301", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "經濟學概論與財政學概論", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年特種考試地方政府公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 12, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "locality", "civil_category": "財經廉政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('locality-1fb53453-moex-00277', 'locality-1fb53453', 'locality-1fb53453-moex-110-51f0585d', 'sub-locality-1fb53453-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '已知甲的所得為$50,000，假設甲有0.1的機率生病，生病時的所得為$20,000，確定等值（certainty equivalent）為$46,500。在完全保險的情形下，甲的精算公平保險費（actuarially fair insurance premium）為何？', '["$2,000", "$3,000", "$3,500", "$4,500"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:34:35+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "9a3f62f137b0", "answer_pdf_sha1": "d6448fd149c5", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110190", "c": "317", "s": "1301", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "經濟學概論與財政學概論", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年特種考試地方政府公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 13, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "locality", "civil_category": "財經廉政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('locality-1fb53453-moex-00278', 'locality-1fb53453', 'locality-1fb53453-moex-110-51f0585d', 'sub-locality-1fb53453-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '假設在完全競爭市場下，某一財貨有外部利益（externalbenefits）產生，則在市場均衡時，下列敘 述何者正確？', '["邊際社會利益大於邊際社會成本", "邊際社會利益等於邊際社會成本", "邊際社會利益等於邊際私人利益", "邊際私人利益大於邊際私人成本"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:34:35+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "9a3f62f137b0", "answer_pdf_sha1": "d6448fd149c5", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110190", "c": "317", "s": "1301", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "經濟學概論與財政學概論", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年特種考試地方政府公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 14, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "locality", "civil_category": "財經廉政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('locality-1fb53453-moex-00279', 'locality-1fb53453', 'locality-1fb53453-moex-110-51f0585d', 'sub-locality-1fb53453-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '根據相等比例犧牲（Equalproportionalsacrifice）原則，假設所得邊際效用固定，當所有人的效用 函數都相同且效用水準只決定於所得，此時所得稅應採何種稅率課徵？', '["累進稅率", "比例稅率", "累退稅率", "先課累進稅再課比例稅"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:34:35+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "9a3f62f137b0", "answer_pdf_sha1": "d6448fd149c5", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110190", "c": "317", "s": "1301", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "經濟學概論與財政學概論", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年特種考試地方政府公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 15, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "locality", "civil_category": "財經廉政"}'::jsonb, NULL)
